# IDE plugin install artifacts (generated by specgate plugins install — machine-specific)
# .agents/ holds machine-specific Codex install output (ignored at every level),
# EXCEPT the committed repo-root marketplace pointer
# (/.agents/plugins/marketplace.json -> ./plugins) that lets others add this repo
# as a Codex marketplace. The exception is anchored to the repo root so nested
# .agents/ dirs (e.g. install artifacts under app/) stay ignored.
.agents/
!/.agents/
/.agents/*
!/.agents/plugins/
/.agents/plugins/*
!/.agents/plugins/marketplace.json
!app/cli/internal/command/local_plugin_assets/.agents/
!app/cli/internal/command/local_plugin_assets/.agents/plugins/
!app/cli/internal/command/local_plugin_assets/.agents/plugins/marketplace.json
!app/cli/internal/command/local_plugin_assets/.agents/plugins/personal-marketplace.json
CLAUDE.specgate.md
AGENTS.specgate.md
.codex/
